{"tid":59553,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"業權壟斷 香港首10名擁逾4萬單位","createTime":"2016-12-29T17:37:51.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-29T19:12:40.000Z","uid":10101,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9eca8fb8aebdfe5abaf8c7b05823b8c8e0101dfb","tid":59553,"uid":10101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T17:37:51.000Z","msg":"香港業權壟斷有多嚴重？根據一項調查，香港首10名差餉納稅人已擁有超過4萬單位，首100名更擁有7.9萬個。調查指香港沒有對空置物業作懲罰，是空置的主因。<br />\n<br />\n根據「本土研究社」對本港空置物業的調查，2014年官方數字反映，香港交差餉最多的法人，第一名已擁有近1.7萬個單位，首10名擁有超過4萬個，首100名更擁有7.9萬個。兩組數字，相等於2014年《施政報告》中提及2009至13年5年間，共建4.8萬個私營單位，及公營單位數目7.5萬相約。<br />\n<br />\n報告指，大量空置單位湧現，實因香港對空置單位沒有成本，導致大業主有條件空置、囤積及炒賣單位，屬結構性因素之一。<br />\n<br />\n對於官方不斷宣傳覓地建屋，但報告質疑無助香港人解決居住問題，反而會加劇「有人冇屋住，有屋冇人住」，大量房屋空置的情況。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.memehk.com/posts/5062#sthash.D3CmJvHE.dpuf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.memehk.com%2Fposts%2F5062%23sthash.D3CmJvHE.dpuf&d=dzibybXEdBHwvSxBIQK5X2N6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=d576239f\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.memehk.com/posts/5062#sthash.D3CmJvHE.dpuf</a>"},{"pid":"07e6a2372644ed66c5cfd914fea65a6995ad204e","tid":59553,"uid":62514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T18:06:31.000Z","msg":"1.7萬個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1dba8886ce61fda6bf7cb86170fff75a7ed15670","tid":59553,"uid":3818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T18:07:37.000Z","msg":"收租都收到手軟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af92331d46e068962b74a39827d08323935c5e6c","tid":59553,"uid":15262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T18:23:57.000Z","msg":"癲"},{"pid":"bf312e3c2bee740650960a70bfaf30adc692d3d5","tid":59553,"uid":64582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0